<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>tā míng shì yé hé huá 迦南178</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 rén de shēng mìng shéi zhǔ zǎi wǒ zhī dào shì yé hé huá,
 hēi yè dào bái tiān shéi zhǎng guǎn wǒ zhī dào shì yé hé huá,
 hào hào huán yǔ máng máng dà de dōu shǔ yé hé huá,
 de de shēn chù dōu shǔ tā, wàn yǒu dōu shǔ tā,
 pǔ tiān xià de wàn mín dōu yào rèn shì tā.
 pǔ tiān xià de wàn mín dōu yào jìng wèi tā.
 tā de míng zì shì zì yǒu yǒng yǒu,
 tā de míng zì shì yé hé huá, yé hé huá.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>178</hymn_number>
</song>